.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, grapefruit, grapes, lettuce, pomegranate, pumpkin
7 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, hamster, frog, dog, rat, ferret
1. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating pomegranate and the owner of the rat##2
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person eating grapes is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | lettuce | grapefruit | pomegranate | cauliflower | pumpkin | apple      | grapes  |
| Pet   | rat | frog  | ferret     | hamster     | dog  | snake | lizard |

