.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: jazz, salsa, classical, pop, ambient, dubstep, house
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, polish
 1. the fan of house is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the fan of ambient is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 6. the mexican is between the fan of classical and the pakistani##2
 7. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
 8. the mexican is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 9. the fan of salsa is the chinese##1
10. the australian is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Music-Genre      | classical    | ambient  | pop  | jazz  | house      | dubstep       | salsa |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | pakistani | polish | australian | malaysian | chinese  |

