.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, paramedic, pilot, project-manager, scientist, videographer, writer
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, tram, scooter, subway, skateboard, airplane, car
1. the pilot is on the left of the writer##1
2. the person driving the scooter is the scientist##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the videographer is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the car is between the person driving the skateboard and the firefighter##2
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the videographer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | scientist | firefighter | project-manager | videographer | paramedic | pilot     | writer |
| Transport   | scooter   | subway    | car    | skateboard      | tram  | helicopter | airplane |

