.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, skateboard, helicopter, scooter, car, subway
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, parkour, rowing, rugby, surfing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person driving the scooter##2
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Transport   | motorbike | bus    | helicopter | skateboard   | car | subway    | scooter |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | volleyball    | cycling | rugby    | parkour | surfing  |

