 5. the photographer is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
 7. the dressmaker is on the right of the police-officer##1
 8. the accountant is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is sailing##2
11. the photographer is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
