.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, disaster, horror, romance, satire, thriller
There 7 different types of food: strawberry, pepper, grapefruit, cherry, garlic, raspberry, cranberry
1. the person watching action movies is the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is between the person eating cranberry and the person eating garlic##2
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | satire | romance | disaster | thriller  | action |
| Food     | grapefruit | cherry | garlic   | strawberry     | cranberry    | pepper | raspberry   |

