.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
City: venice, rome, boston, hannover, london, hamburg, san-francisco
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, sailing, skateboarding, tennis, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person traveling to rome##2
7. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
9. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| City   | san-francisco | hamburg       | boston    | london | hannover | rome     | venice       |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | skateboarding | volleyball | tennis        | sailing | ice-hockey | weightlifting |

