The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, folk, house, pop, punk, reggae, salsa
 1. the havana-smoker is the fan of salsa##1
 2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 3. the havana-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the fan of disco##2
 4. the montecristo-smoker is between the blend-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of house##1
 6. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is the fan of punk##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
10. the fan of pop is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Cigar   | oliveros | havana | aristoff  | ritmeester   | montecristo | blend | davidoff |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | salsa       | disco | house | reggae  | folk   | punk   |

