 5. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the person eating lime is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 7. the fan of house is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
