.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-15::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, mirinda, water
There are 7 different favourite colors: red, grey, coral, pink, amber, azure, green
 1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking water and the person who likes red##2
 5. the person who likes pink is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person who likes green is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person who likes coral is the person who likes coral##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
10. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | fanta       | mirinda | milk      | hot-chocolate | water       | iced-tea | lemonade |
| Color       | azure | coral    | amber | green    | grey | pink   | red |

